  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency expect to v21",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest\">expect</a> from <code>v1.20.2</code> to <code>v21.1.0</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>facebook/jest</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"2110\">21.1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/13e4ba299d57c65248a5cd763bb66f59b3b24902\"><code>13e4ba2</code></a> v21.1.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/8529bd1582da94584a7213d013f8858bbffa7938\"><code>8529bd1</code></a> Call jest-diff and pretty-format more precisely in toHaveProperty matcher (#&#8203;4445)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/6414c5d1eaad7f4f38c17b078aaedb2d7eb3bde1\"><code>6414c5d</code></a> fix Map equality test (#&#8203;4404)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/8bc795ccab6d2ca02712d94b3210959746c31be8\"><code>8bc795c</code></a> Allow chaining mockClear and mockReset (#&#8203;4475)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/105f7db4a13f80449c37881622719099ad915703\"><code>105f7db</code></a> Improve docs (#&#8203;4478)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/c4844a66ceec221573363e0ad8059e05fb8e4e59\"><code>c4844a6</code></a> Flatten temporary data structures in jest-diff (#&#8203;4469)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/72af99d25d6478d2000c929eb821f9bf0489f16d\"><code>72af99d</code></a> Make FUNCTION_NAME_RESERVED_PATTERN stateless (#&#8203;4466)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/19b5cce80d4ddb69864222b84164d09120cbf898\"><code>19b5cce</code></a> [jest-mock] fix function name cleaning when making mock fn (#&#8203;4464)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/213634d7021f646ad9bc2e18f43dfef0d05d6e37\"><code>213634d</code></a> Expose restoreAllMocks to  object (#&#8203;4463)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/9c429cd15d639ab42cfe0a9fa7032095af3b675f\"><code>9c429cd</code></a> Use ES module exports (#&#8203;4454)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/b621cd2b52122690f51bfe6afe7ab5e93761306e\"><code>b621cd2</code></a> Create README.md with documentation and usage (#&#8203;4457)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/215e1d4d38e073bbd62c5b4e52e991374fc1ea62\"><code>215e1d4</code></a> Changelog for 21.0.1 and 21.0.2</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"2102\">21.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/9b6ff26eb3c0f03215c5fc52d3842c3d56d55ef0\"><code>9b6ff26</code></a> v21.0.2</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/fab01c71680fc54f21ba0aa7ca65acc8d8ff9523\"><code>fab01c7</code></a> Take precedence of NODE_PATH when resolving node_modules directories (#&#8203;4453)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/6b484db69b130173dcf2f60ef7f8a1abb7f7a521\"><code>6b484db</code></a> --silent flag (#&#8203;4450)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/76f018d1e7f4f08b9391a409eeb8d1b3f364d438\"><code>76f018d</code></a> Update own deps (#&#8203;4441)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/16431b5ae65660090a4d4c71f6aca02e733ac62e\"><code>16431b5</code></a> Fix race condition with --coverage and babel-jest identical file contents edge case (#&#8203;4432)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/2c910dcaab6d6809966ed9c80441fd23e5cf606d\"><code>2c910dc</code></a> Add extra parameter: runTestsByPath. Fixes #&#8203;4396 (#&#8203;4411)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/4398ccbf59c760a1c182480899856b928fc27c4f\"><code>4398ccb</code></a> Upgrade all outdated deps (#&#8203;4425)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/0cb03f6474f52964ed74eadcde2ae3e219b4d04e\"><code>0cb03f6</code></a> Upgrade to prettier 1.6 (#&#8203;4426)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/15173910cdd77beee1298ac1620079a49c627393\"><code>1517391</code></a> Update Jest&#x27;s own dependency on the eslint plugin (#&#8203;4424)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/9075ecf0774fc29ba9c5e4bdbceca0d9774a793c\"><code>9075ecf</code></a> v21.0.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/a8be52b34d4259e8a8635dad8025f85d9d5391ab\"><code>a8be52b</code></a> Remove existing throw (#&#8203;4417)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"2100\">21.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/be4bec387d90ac8d6a7596be88bf8e4994bc3ed9\"><code>be4bec3</code></a> v21.0.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/f3e2bd3a021e59763004ab2dd3f52eee647d61e3\"><code>f3e2bd3</code></a> Jest 21 Changelog</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/0e76e689cf052f2c6b3db917ccb9107567fdba6a\"><code>0e76e68</code></a> Fix React PropTypes warning in tests for Immutable plugin (#&#8203;4412)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/be6952dd9a4f4646a00aa0467f07b6fed9c4a12f\"><code>be6952d</code></a> Add displayName to TestResult (#&#8203;4408)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/a344d497160e4ab8f8e8a1d122395a4a52a3ce61\"><code>a344d49</code></a> Make listTests always print to console.log (#&#8203;4391)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/de74b38aff9f0a91dcdaf5986d2a6f963b78cfdf\"><code>de74b38</code></a> Allow custom resolver to be used with[out] moduleNameMapper (#&#8203;4174)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/7e2c206364bb8d0b3e09b877dd658efc5c27458b\"><code>7e2c206</code></a> Ignore indentation of data structures in jest-diff (#&#8203;3429)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/fab51f8a57748a3d2af7d77ee2268c0232da5270\"><code>fab51f8</code></a> fix(babel): Support upcoming beta (#&#8203;4403)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/e926ab806327049588d89f356880f11748c8cec3\"><code>e926ab8</code></a> Update TypeScript + Jest getting started (#&#8203;4392)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/60b93b9f2ebcbc40f89c4487dff01bb0a368cc5d\"><code>60b93b9</code></a> fix(babel): Handle ignored files in babel v7 (#&#8203;4393)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/0b7b47be1d739ae51faa979e8a5278088a607e1d\"><code>0b7b47b</code></a> Specify watchPathIgnorePatterns will only be available in Jest 21+ (#&#8203;4398)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/24a61bb1aa310d92208833c33fa6fb8b1cfe4d2c\"><code>24a61bb</code></a> Use Jest Types inside Jest Editor Support (#&#8203;4385)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/dfdca8b115a8d484c8e8b00cf3ceab7d54919ba1\"><code>dfdca8b</code></a> Don&#x27;t format node assert errors when there&#x27;s no &#x27;assert&#x27; module (#&#8203;4376)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/51e0a2494233c1e132e5e016646e941ca7afd647\"><code>51e0a24</code></a> Add fake chalk in browser builds in order to support IE10 (#&#8203;4367)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/e5fd7733cafaa1e8b59191476951df2a4d740d49\"><code>e5fd773</code></a> Use &quot;verbose&quot; no test found message when there is only one project (#&#8203;4378)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/17cdf536392c8294ecde3f7e36a79d783fbbd436\"><code>17cdf53</code></a> Remove .dim from displayName for better readability (#&#8203;4377)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/a3ed98085be4906abe5107589ba051055dba89a2\"><code>a3ed980</code></a> Change Promise detection code in jest-circus to support non-global Promise implementations (#&#8203;4375)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/e5356658e6bcf6f31aa26b8a0db7b602ba3ece7d\"><code>e535665</code></a> Add displayName to MPR (#&#8203;4327)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/39f83a99eb426a853a5369d194193bbc30ecf3aa\"><code>39f83a9</code></a> Separated the snapshot summary creation from the printing to improve testability. (#&#8203;4373)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/cb8e760041a5d5d0e59fcf7d7b7f440365412755\"><code>cb8e760</code></a> Improved the jest reporter with snapshot info per test. (#&#8203;3660)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/e4278b340b5460fde7a908b47dd05fb5ac3e90c8\"><code>e4278b3</code></a> fix typescript jest test crash (#&#8203;4363)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/559e70d4866ac3ccfe7ebed60a1dedceb3e53b0d\"><code>559e70d</code></a> Flow upgrade (#&#8203;4355)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/e81a5e55bf377b78f1901ed19d8c8a7e9f43a5a8\"><code>e81a5e5</code></a> Remove redundant yarn.lock entry in npmignores (#&#8203;4368)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/77251b9673d806412ac665605baaa9a82f561f52\"><code>77251b9</code></a> Add missing watchify dependency (#&#8203;4366)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/db4465e6bd0195ef95540e3a068882361cc67682\"><code>db4465e</code></a> Fix appveyor (#&#8203;4353)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/19384094dc7ac5cd77e4eacf611d76abe5837063\"><code>1938409</code></a> Return UNDEFINED for undefined type in ReactElement plugin (#&#8203;4360)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/96ba36f3ebb6c4b5a7f3d07253cb3757255aac88\"><code>96ba36f</code></a> Rename HTMLElement as DOMElement plugin (#&#8203;4361)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/44b1c6d1de6b7666c8fa22986d192d67fee2191a\"><code>44b1c6d</code></a> Unified &#x27;no tests found&#x27; message for non-verbose MPR (#&#8203;4354)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/f509856258499bdfa4b1bb43016652b9acd86b81\"><code>f509856</code></a> Fix bad merge.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/8bdafbb297b6179f975a22f8e46e0c8d4f00f775\"><code>8bdafbb</code></a> Fix nits.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/jest/commit/6323e64b5ebe1dd547f3085d08bce1412c912043\"><code>6323e64</code></a> Updated config doc with info on glob coverage thresholds (#&#8203;4350)</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
